<li id="cite_note-Christ_And_Culture_Revisited-160"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Christ_And_Culture_Revisited_160-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Christ_And_Culture_Revisited_160-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFCarson,_D._A.2008" class="citation book cs1">Carson, D. A. (2008). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://books.google.com/books?id=pIwE74bxvpAC"><i>Christ And Culture Revisited</i></a>. Wm. B. Eerdmans Publishing. p.&#160;189. <a href="/wiki/ISBN_(identifier)" class="mw-redirect" title="ISBN (identifier)">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0802831743" title="Special:BookSources/978-0802831743"><bdi>978-0802831743</bdi></a>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20160512113715/https://books.google.com/books?id=pIwE74bxvpAC&amp;dq">Archived</a> from the original on 12 May 2016.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Christ+And+Culture+Revisited&amp;rft.pages=189&amp;rft.pub=Wm.+B.+Eerdmans+Publishing&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft.isbn=978-0802831743&amp;rft.au=Carson%2C+D.+A.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DpIwE74bxvpAC&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASeparation+of+church+and+state" class="Z3988"></span></span>
</li>
